  • Field Details

    • cardType

      private PlayableCardType cardType
      This attribute represents card type: Initial, Resource or Gold

    • frontGridConfiguration

      private Corner[][] frontGridConfiguration
      This attribute represents a 2x2 matrix used to store information about the four front corners of the card. A corner can be NotAvailableCorner, EmptyCorner or can contain a Symbol

    • requiredSymbolToPlace

      private HashMap<Symbol,Integer> requiredSymbolToPlace
      Symbols and quantity that a player needs to have to place the card in the CardOrientation.UP state in his station.

    • backGridConfiguration

      private Corner[][] backGridConfiguration
      This attribute represents a 2x2 matrix used to store information about the four back corners of the card. A corner can be NotAvailableCorner, EmptyCorner or can contain a Symbol

    • permanentResources

      private ArrayList<Symbol> permanentResources
      This attribute represents permanent resources positioned at the center of the back of the card. This resource can not be covered.

    • cardState

      private PlayableCard.CardState cardState
      This attribute represents the state of a card, if it is on the front or on the back.

    • playableEffect

      private PlayableEffect playableEffect
      This attribute represents the effect that a playable card has, that is activated when the card is positioned in a station in the UP state. To see various effects, see classes that implements PlayableEffect
